data.name: Pumpkin Seed Energy Bites
data.quickTastyDescription: Nutritious and delicious no-bake energy bites packed with pumpkin seeds and sweetened with honey.
detailedCookingInstructions: In a mixing bowl, combine the rolled oats, pumpkin seeds, honey, peanut butter, chocolate chips, and vanilla extract.
Mix well until all ingredients are thoroughly combined.
Using your hands, form small balls (about 1 inch in diameter) from the mixture.
Place the energy bites on a parchment-lined tray.
Refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to firm up before serving.
data.modifiersForBase: Pumpkin seeds and oats for a nutritious boost
